

^y = B0 + B1X1 + B2X2 ... + BnXn

RSS - equals the sum from i=1 to n of (yi - ^yi)^2

B1 (coefficient of x) - sum from i=1 to n of (yi - ybar (avg)) * (xi - xbar) / sum from i=1 to n of (xi - xbar)^2 

B0 (intercept) - ybar - B1xbar

Use RSS formula to estimate B1 & B0

SE for B0 & B1 

RSE = sqrt(RSS / (n - 2))

t-statistic = (B1 - 0 (H0)) / SE(B1)

Var(error) = RSE^2
